{"word":"ἀντίτυπος","slug":"ἀντίτυπος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀντίτυπος, ον</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀντί\">ἀντί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τύπος\">τύπος</a></el> ‘impression’ made by a stamping device such as a seal <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> <el>τυπέω</el> ‘strike’; <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀντί\">ἀντί</a></el> has the force of ‘in turn’, <i>i.e.</i> the stamping device strikes back a copy of itself]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a><b><i>in corresponding manner,</i></b> defining <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βάπτισμα\">βάπτισμα</a></el> <b><a href='B:670 3:21'>1 Pt 3:21</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> as noun <el>τὸ ἀντίτυπον</el>, <b><i>representation, copy</i> <a href='B:650 9:24'>Hb 9:24</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀντιτάσσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀντίχριστος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}